{"tid":1636534,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"Hong Kong protest slogan","createTime":"2019-10-07T18:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T18:27:10.000Z","uid":4092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7e456d62436a522e1f1cd9b8e274ac97e37f674f","tid":1636534,"uid":4092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:25:44.000Z","msg":"I would like to teach you some slogan for the protest in Hong Kong<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFirst one <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">five demands, not one less</span> remember it should be&rdquo;not&rdquo; one less. <br />\n<br />\nSecond<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: blue;\">Free Hong Kong, democracy now！</span><br />\n<br />\nThird<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <span style=\"color: purple;\">fight for freedom, stand with Hong Kong </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />welcome to add more slogan below in order to let the world know our slogan<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1d5cbcac3adb89b43e51977cdb203d9262bfbb","tid":1636534,"uid":189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZrPTLm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZrPTLm.jpg&h=379834e2&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}